{"word":"ὀψέ","slug":"ὀψέ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n76295\" key=\"o)ye/\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀψέ</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aeol.\">Aeol.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὄψι</orth> (q. v.), <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <sense id=\"n76295.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">after a long time, at length, late</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔκ τε καὶ ὀ. τελεῖ</foreign>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὐτίκα</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:161\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.161</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀ. κακῶς ἔλθοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:534\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.534</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀ. διδάσκεσθαι, μανθάνειν</foreign>, to be <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">late</tr_> in learning, learn <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">too late</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:1425\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1425</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1264\" default=\"NO\" TEIfo